\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Do you ever remember punishing them at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Or your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Oh no - he didn't - he wouldn't. I never - he'd never - he never went like that to them, no, never. An
d when - as soon as ever Bessie was - er - I don't know how old she was - he taught her to play chess - taught her to play whist and he had - they had - er - a pack of cards that they called - er - oh what was that game they called it - oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Snap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 No, no, it was further than snap - be - oh I'll ask Edna if she comes in. I think we've got the cards now in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 It wasn't happy families or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Oh no. Oh no. It was further advanced than happy families. He - he taught - he taught Bessie to play - or - pontoon - yes.
