\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Well, I don't know - in the days - we knew what was right and wrong and I think they must have copied it.
