No. Well, I - I used to let them play - go out to play. I used to let Bessie. Of course, as I say, with Edna, she - she only seemed to play with her cousins. They all played together - she never was an only one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 When they had a birthday would it be different from any other day - did you buy them presents and did they have a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Oh - I used to make parties for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Did they have presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Oh sometimes. Probably bring them a bit of something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Did they have a party with special food and friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 Yes. I've made lots of parties - for them.
