\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14228208 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 But when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3305828 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 
 did any of you play instruments - did your husband play one or your children?
