\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 If we went out any - I - had a friend that lived at Moulton - oh his sister lived at Moulton too - he used to take her - take them there.

