\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454056 EM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid936107\charrsid9916195 
I think perhaps they must have been. Oh yes. It seemed as though they could get jobs at night and - some - er - pubs and places like that. I believe. Waiting on a night or two a week at some Hotel or Pub - they got jobs.
